\subsection{Description field in knowls}
\begin{definition}\label{doc.knowl.description}
\uses{doc.knowl.context_free,doc.knowl.naming_conventions,doc.knowl.naming_suggestions}
The description field in a Knowl serves as the most accurate description of the Knowl {{ KNOWL('doc.knowl.context_free', "outside of any context")}}. It is a human-readable version of the Knowl, compliant with the naming {{ KNOWL('doc.knowl.naming_conventions', "conventions") }} and {{ KNOWL('doc.knowl.naming_suggestions', "suggestions") }}.
\end{definition}


